show.title: Detective of the Republic: Chasing the Killer
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/h4FQrQXa2ee2EsVV7
show.description: A poor young man had just been fired by his boss and was feeling dejected. Suddenly, he was transported into a novel he had been engrossed in, called "Detective of the Republic: Chasing the Killer". He miraculously transformed into a famous detective in the novel. Coincidentally, a murder case occurred in the city; a dancer at the Phoenix Dance Hall was mysteriously killed. He and his team went to investigate the case, only to find it linked to another murder case from six years ago. Let's see how this ordinary man, turned renowned detective, solves the case...
